Moving on, what does this mean for Patrick Mahomes (8:00)? Is Travis Kelce the clear #1 TE in Fantasy now (18:00)? And would you rather have Jaylen Waddle or Juju Smith-Schuster (19:15)? How about Tua Tagovailoa vs. the Year 2 QBs (25:10)? At the end of theÂ Podcast, we talk about what this trade means for the Chiefs franchise and the NFC West in general.
